Steps I took to install SASS

1. Installed node version 20.16 in my ubuntu terminal

$ curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash

2. Installed SASS in my terminal, using:

npm install sass -v 3.7.4 OR  npm install -g sass

3. Verified SASS Installation

sass --version

4. I created a .scss file and compiled it using:

sass 0-debug_log.scss style.css

5. To automatically update the CSS file whenever I saved changes, I ran:

sass --watch style.scss:style.css
